Text: Allegheny DASHESare the revised DASHES for the two Allegheny Deals These are very similar to what has already circulated The relevant differences between this version and the previous version are Exclusion of June from Coverage Lower system strike price set at ATM at deal closing close Total package price dropped from MM to MM Lower mean losses and lower P Any questions please call me at Larry
